RICHMOND CYCLING STRATEGY CONSULTATION
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The London Borough of Richmond upon Thames has one of the highest
    proportions of people cycling in London (7% of journeys). However,
    there is still more that can be done to inspire people to cycle and
    make it safer for all. Whether you cycle or not we would like
    to hear your views on how we can improve cycling in Richmond
    borough. Your comments will help us understand what we need to do
    to get more people cycling.

